{"tid":1922190,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓總理指習近平仍可能如期訪韓","createTime":"2020-03-12T12:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T12:14:42.000Z","uid":75656,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"baa03cc968f628672c6b6543cb630e86c9fde345","tid":1922190,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:08:34.000Z","msg":"南韓國務總理丁世均就中國國家主席習近平訪韓的可能性表示，認為這取決於南韓境內新型冠狀病毒疫情管控情況。<br />\n<br />\n習近平訪問日本計劃告吹，訪韓之行也成疑問，丁世均稱，習近平近日訪問湖北省，可以說武漢疫情已經得到控制，相信習近平訪問南韓一事，目前仍有可能。<br />\n<br />\n中韓原定安排習近平和國務院總理李克強，分別於上半年和下半年訪韓，着手討論未來30年合作願景。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2400534/%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%E7%B8%BD%E7%90%86%E6%8C%87%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E4%BB%8D%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%A6%82%E6%9C%9F%E8%A8%AA%E9%9F%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2400534%2F%25E5%258D%2597%25E9%259F%2593%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E4%25BB%258D%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%25A6%2582%25E6%259C%259F%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E9%259F%2593&d=xKwzLSQbN%2FgnQ4qVdIYE%2BMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=1ef5ff76\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2400534/%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%E7%B8%BD%E7%90%86%E6%8C%87%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E4%BB%8D%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E5%A6%82%E6%9C%9F%E8%A8%AA%E9%9F%93</a>"},{"pid":"111ded618e00100c2f344fbc5048017ea1bc8253","tid":1922190,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b422732f045eeb916f41bc0a7148f68b206c41bb","tid":1922190,"uid":298012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T12:14:42.000Z","msg":"求武肺經韓仔反cup習敗北<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" c